01/05/2006
JASENOVAC, Croatia -- A ceremony commemorating the 61st anniversary of the liberation of inmates at the WWII Jasenovac concentration camp -- known as the Croatian Auschwitz -- was held at the Jasenovac memorial area on Sunday (30 April). President Stipe Mesic attended with other government officials, as well as camp survivors and representatives of victims' families. Thousands of Serbs, Jews and Roma died at the camp. (Vecernji list - 01/04/06; HINA, index.hr - 30/04/06)
